overview:
“My Doctor” - this is information Internet portal, dedicated to medicine, health and beauty.

“My Doctor” will help visitors obtain information about doctors of various medical specialties, the hospitals and clinics, beauty salons and fitness centers. Students can find a school, find a useful information, or by publishing their articles. For continuously updated information base allows the visitor of the portal quickly and easily find the necessary information on the location, services, as well as complete contact information.
